ing equilibrium magnetic field. Overall, this\nunderstanding supports the use of flow-free scalings with slight modifications\nto study tearing in a forming sheet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Nov 2017 16:40:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Feb 2018 20:59:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-02"}
