 can be used to learn more about characteristics of the clumpy\nstructure and to test the outflow model, when utilizing high-resolution spectra\nand photoionization model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Nov 2017 16:49:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-27"}
